      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">The Challenge</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Learning the precise patterns for conducting is a foundational skill for any music student or ensemble leader. Traditionally, this is taught using 2D diagrams in textbooks, which can be difficult to translate into fluid, three-dimensional motion.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">The Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">ConductVR provides an immersive practice room where students can learn and master these patterns. With clear visual guides and a simple interface, the application makes the abstract tangible, allowing users to trace patterns in 3D space with their own hands.</p>
